From bf5c5cd58a8672f7d6e10791ee9c8194e3a1501e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vibhav Pant <vibhavp@gmail.com>
Date: Mon, 3 Nov 2025 17:37:29 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 24/63] msvcrt: Call the destructor for C++ exceptions in
 __C_specific_handler.

---
 dlls/msvcr100/msvcr100.spec  |   2 +-
 dlls/msvcr110/msvcr110.spec  |   2 +-
 dlls/msvcr120/msvcr120.spec  |   2 +-
 dlls/msvcr80/msvcr80.spec    |   2 +-
 dlls/msvcr90/msvcr90.spec    |   2 +-
 dlls/msvcrt/except.c         | 253 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 dlls/msvcrt/except_arm.c     |   8 ++
 dlls/msvcrt/except_arm64.c   |  29 ++++
 dlls/msvcrt/except_arm64ec.c |  30 +++++
 dlls/msvcrt/msvcrt.spec      |   2 +-
 dlls/ucrtbase/ucrtbase.spec  |   2 +-
 11 files changed, 327 insertions(+), 7 deletions(-)

